{"tid":1070501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸妹疑紅公仔亂過馬路 遭貨車撞低重創昏迷","createTime":"2019-03-20T16:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T10:30:42.000Z","uid":122,"like":410,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"9721163a3618df40e1c66d0b0a584ed641a5421f","tid":1070501,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190320/large/1553077439_a9d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190320%2Flarge%2F1553077439_a9d9.jpg&h=c58bf729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【17:55】現場解封，車龍有待消散。<br />\n<br />\n油麻地發生交通意外，下午4時許，現場為彌敦道近佐敦道交界，據報一部貨車撞倒一名20歲內地女子，她重創卧地。救援人員接報到場，將傷者送往伊利沙伯醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n在現場附近上班的讀者陳先生表示，工作期間聽到街上傳出巨響，他跑出店外查看，赫見一名女子倒卧馬路邊，失去知覺，一名熱心外籍男子上前安撫傷者，未幾救護員及警員亦到場。<br />\n<br />\n據現場目擊者透露，事發時見該名女子突然衝出馬路，當時為紅公仔，她甫步出馬路，即被駛至的貨車撞倒，飛彈數米。<br />\n<br />\n受事件影響，彌敦道往尖沙嘴方向近佐敦道的快線及中線一度封閉。"},{"pid":"d7c352d8898c1988a259ef7d91622a2ebb4c1f11","tid":1070501,"uid":175661,"like":273,"dislike":10,"score":263,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:45:51.000Z","msg":"一名熱心外籍男子上前安撫傷者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eee1cd0055a66ecafff2581e999d2c07c3a8304","tid":1070501,"uid":85552,"like":221,"dislike":3,"score":218,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:52:52.000Z","msg":"rip司機"},{"pid":"cddaf8f345efb790594cb28b7543ffc0d36920bb","tid":1070501,"uid":144,"like":76,"dislike":24,"score":52,"quote":{"pid":"d7c352d8898c1988a259ef7d91622a2ebb4c1f11","tid":1070501,"uid":175661,"like":273,"dislike":10,"score":263,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:45:51.000Z","msg":"一名熱心外籍男子上前安撫傷者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:53:43.000Z","msg":"對腳幾正 我都想去撫下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f17ab626457a6eb9b96800e8def8255f93d84cb","tid":1070501,"uid":41818,"like":48,"dislike":3,"